A state of assigning the privilege
==============================
Every one of us distribute our privilege to many of object/ energy /humans in different ways. Time to time when they access these privilege then if we ready to pay then there are cool state but if we don't ready to pay then the same privilege create war zone(रन क्षेत्र ) between us and the source of access it.

This same scenario not arise rarely but the same arise many times in our entire life of journey. We unable to find from where it get created and how to overcome with this.
It may be possible the same scenario not always come in front of us exactly form the same source but the similar scenario come mostly since it just get changed their state and we unable to detect their pattern.

Different source of accessing privilege may have different state but if we are not ready to pay then they all privileges create war zone, it may be the bar zone having different significance but war zone is for fight only in first site.

How we assign privilege?
------------------------------
To external source:-

When we feel lack of energy/satisfaction/healing then our senses/mind automatically run/search here and there in search of energy and if it find/pointing some source from where it may
look some chance for the same. Then mind try to interact with that source if it get a access authority from that source then mind try to access some energy/object since at the starting state when mind try to run/search here and there is due to lack of energy ie means it has expectation of energy from external sources.

Till one have expectation for energy from external source, up to this state things are not in control but it is with us only, but when we get fulfill of expectation from external sources the same time the expectation get transform in to privilege.

When we get fulfilled of our expectation and get little happiness then it seems our expectation get lost but not, it get transform into privilege and assign to whom from where we fulfill our expectation.
Later when they access the privilege if we ready to pay then it is cool and when we not ready to pay then begin fight between us and privilege.

***From one hand our expectation get fulfill and from another hand the same expectation get transformed in to privilege and get and assigned to some one else***

To internal source:
When our expectation is from within then it not simply come in fulfill state, you can't get touch with inner self energy simply just having expectation.
Here the within energy is so powerful it always kill/burn our expectation. There is only one way to supply more and more energy to inner self and when we are capable to supply
energy to within then we are not in lack of energy and there is a continuous production of energy using our work out with us.

When our internal abstract energy get activated and we get much more satisfaction/healing then our privilege get assigned to inner self and from here our journey get controlled by/from within and that is central source of energy. When we get realization about within energy then automatically our existence
gating transform towards within using the rout..senses->mind->observation->realization->understanding->streaming....so on.
by using continuous supply of energy under the guidance of observation.

***It is so easy to assign privilege to external source but it is not easy to assign privilege to within**** 

